---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
  year: 'numeric',
  month: 'long',
  day: 'numeric',
});
---

<BaseLayout title="Now" description="What I'm doing now.">
  <div class="py-12 md:py-20 max-w-2xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">Now</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="prose space-y-12">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">What I'm Working On</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li>
            Building a personal knowledge management system to better document and share
            what I learn.
          </li>
          <li>
            Exploring the intersection of first-principles thinking and decision-making in
            uncertain environments.
          </li>
          <li>
            Experimenting with different writing formats and mediums to find what resonates
            with readers.
          </li>
          <li>
            Refining my toolkit and workflow—constantly testing new applications and
            optimizing for focus.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Currently Reading</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li>
            <strong>"Thinking, Fast and Slow"</strong> by Daniel Kahneman — Understanding
            how we make decisions and the biases that influence us.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>"The Courage to Be Disliked"</strong> — A dialogue about psychology,
            freedom, and how to live authentically.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>"Essays by Paul Graham"</strong> — On startups, technology, and what
            it means to do good work.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Thinking About</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li>
            How to make better decisions with incomplete information.
          </li>
          <li>
            The relationship between transparency (building in public) and strategic
            advantage.
          </li>
          <li>
            Creating a sustainable pace of work and creativity rather than burning out.
          </li>
          <li>
            What it means to build something that genuinely matters to people.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Location</h2>
        <p>
          Currently based in a place with good coffee, reliable internet, and quiet spaces
          to focus. I move around occasionally but keep the same core routine.
        </p>
      </section>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 italic pt-8">
        This is a "now" page inspired by{' '}
        <a href="https://nownownow.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          nownownow.com
        </a>
        . It's regularly updated to reflect what's currently occupying my time and attention.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  :global(.prose) {
    color: #333;
  }

  :global(.prose a) {
    color: #2563eb;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  :global(.prose a:hover) {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  :global(.prose h2) {
    color: #0a0a0a;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  :global(.prose ul) {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  :global(.prose li) {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  :global(.prose strong) {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  :global(.prose p) {
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
</style>
